Yakov,

It was my mistake. I have corrected Cantera.msi, so please try it again.

By the way, when you start Cantera.msi after already installing Cantera, it
will ask if you want to repair or uninstall it. Select uninstall. This will
cleanly remove the old version. Then run Cantera.msi again to install the
new version.

Dave
